[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcom.example.HtmlParserFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mHtmlParserFuzzer.jav[0m[1;92ma:40[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA critical OS Command Injection vulnerability has been detected in Apache Tika's [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing functionality. The vulnerability is triggered when processing HTML content [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontaining data URIs, which leads to execution of external parser commands with [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpotentially attacker-controlled data. The issue manifests through a chain of parser[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvocations starting from HTML parsing, through embedded document extraction, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39multimately reaching the ExternalParser component where unsanitized data is passed [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto [0m[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Vulnerability Type[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis is an OS Command Injection vulnerability [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCWE-[0m[1;36m78[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, classified as a critical [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msecurity issue. OS Command Injection occurs when an application executes operating [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msystem commands using data that can be controlled by an attacker, potentially [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mleading to remote code execution, unauthorized system access, or data exfiltration.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Issue Details[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe vulnerability was detected by the Jazzer fuzzer's security instrumentation [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.sanitizers.OsCommandInjection[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m during execution of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe HtmlParserFuzzer test harness. The detection occurred at the point where [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mProcessBuilder.start[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m was invoked with attacker-controlled data, indicating that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexternal command execution is being performed without proper sanitization or [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Execution Flow Analysis[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe stack trace reveals the following execution path:[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Entry Point**: The fuzzer invokes [0m[1;35mHtmlParserFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m which [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls [0m[1;35mparseOne[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **HTML Parsing**: [0m[1;35mAutoDetectParser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is called, which delegates to [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCompositeParser and then JSoupParser for HTML content processing[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **HTML Element Processing**: During HTML parsing, [0m[1;35mHtmlHandler.startElement[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoked to process HTML elements[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Data URI Handling**: The handler encounters and processes a data URI scheme [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvia [0m[1;35mHtmlHandler.handleDataURIScheme[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Embedded Document Extraction**: [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mParsingEmbeddedDocumentExtractor.parseEmbedded[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is called to extract and parse the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39membedded content from the data URI[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Parser Delegation Chain**: The content goes through another round of parser [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mselection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDelegatingParser → AutoDetectParser → CompositeParser[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **External Parser Invocation**: [0m[1;35mExternalParser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is ultimately invoked, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich calls [0m[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to execute an external command[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. **Vulnerability Trigger**: The command execution occurs at [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mProcessBuilder.start[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with unsanitized attacker-controlled input[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Key Observations[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Data URI as Attack Vector**: The vulnerability is specifically triggered [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough HTML data URI schemes, which allows embedding of arbitrary content within [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHTML documents that can then be extracted and processed[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Multiple Parser Layers**: The issue involves multiple layers of parser [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomposition and delegation, suggesting that data flows through several [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransformation stages before reaching the vulnerable execution point[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **External Command Execution**: The ExternalParser component is designed to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoke external system commands for parsing certain file types, but appears to lack[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msufficient input validation[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Embedded Document Processing**: The vulnerability is tied to Tika's capability[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto extract and parse embedded documents, which creates a pathway for malicious [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontent to reach the command execution layer[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas Requiring Investigation[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo gain a comprehensive understanding of this vulnerability, the following [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomponents should be examined:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **ExternalParser.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines around [0m[1;36m274[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m314[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How command strings are constructed from parsed content[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - What input validation and sanitization mechanisms exist[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How command arguments are assembled and passed to [0m[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **HtmlHandler.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m377[0m[39m and surrounding code[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The [0m[1;35mhandleDataURIScheme[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method implementation[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How data URIs are decoded and prepared for embedded document extraction[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - What content type detection occurs before delegation to other parsers[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **ParsingEmbeddedDocumentExtractor.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m101[0m[39m region[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The [0m[1;35mparseEmbedded[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method's logic for handling extracted content[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How metadata and content type information is passed to subsequent parsers[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether any security checks are performed before delegating to other parsers[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Tika Configuration**:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Which external parsers are enabled by default[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - What command templates or patterns are configured for external parser [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvocation[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether there are any built-in security restrictions or sandboxing mechanisms[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Data Flow Path**:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How data extracted from HTML data URIs flows through the parser chain[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - What transformations or encoding/decoding operations occur[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Where attacker-controlled data could be injected into command strings[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m712[0m[39m:                        Integer.TYPE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m713[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35msetLimit.invoke[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmgr, MAX_ENTITY_EXPANSIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m714[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mfactory.setAttribute[0m[1;39m([0m[39mXERCES_SECURITY_MANAGER_PROPERTY, mgr[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m715[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Stop once one can be setup without error[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m716[0m[39m:                return;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m717[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mClassNotFoundException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m718[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m continue without log, this is expected in some setups[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m719[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mThrowable e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m NOSONAR - also catch things like [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNoClassDefError here[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m720[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m throttle the log somewhat as it can spam the log otherwise[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m721[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mSystem.currentTimeMillis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > LAST_LOG + [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mTimeUnit.MINUTES.toMillis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m5[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m722[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m723[0m[39m:                            [0m[32m"SAX Security Manager could not be setup [0m[32m[[0m[32mlog [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32msuppressed for 5 "[0m[39m +[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m724[0m[39m:                                    [0m[32m"minutes[0m[32m][0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m725[0m[39m:                            e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m726[0m[39m:                    LAST_LOG = [0m[1;35mSystem.currentTimeMillis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m727[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m728[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m729[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m730[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m731[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m separate old version of Xerces not found => use the builtin way of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msetting the property[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m732[0m[39m:        try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m733[0m[39m:            [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mfactory.setAttribute[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"http://www.oracle.com/xml/jaxp/properties/entityExpansionLimi[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mt"[0m[39m,[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m734[0m[39m:                    MAX_ENTITY_EXPANSIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m735[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIllegalArgumentException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m736[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m NOSONAR - also catch things like NoClassDefError here[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m737[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m throttle the log somewhat as it can spam the log otherwise[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m738[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mSystem.currentTimeMillis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > LAST_LOG + [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mTimeUnit.MINUTES.toMillis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m5[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m739[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"SAX Security Manager could not be setup [0m[32m[[0m[32mlog [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32msuppressed for 5 minutes[0m[32m][0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m740[0m[39m:                        e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m741[0m[39m:                LAST_LOG = [0m[1;35mSystem.currentTimeMillis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m742[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m743[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m744[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis of the Vulnerability[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the code snippets and evaluation report, I've identified the root [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause and optimal fix strategy for this OS Command Injection vulnerability:[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe vulnerability exists in [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/parser/external/ExternalParser.java` at [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlines [0m[1;36m280[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m318[0m[39m. The issue is:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Unsafe Path Substitution**: File paths from [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mTikaInputStream.getFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` are directly inserted into command strings [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvia `[0m[1;35mString.replace[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m298[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m without any validation or sanitization[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **String Splitting Vulnerability**: When `command.length == [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m`, the command is [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msplit by spaces [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m291[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which can break command structure if paths contain [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecial characters[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with Single String**: Using `[0m[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m312[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvokes a shell on many platforms, which interprets shell metacharacters[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Attack Vector**: HTML data URIs flow through HtmlHandler → [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mParsingEmbeddedDocumentExtractor → DelegatingParser → CompositeParser → [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExternalParser, where unsanitized temporary file paths are used in command [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstruction[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Key Observations from Code Analysis[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mProcessUtils.escapeCommandLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Only handles Windows spaces, NOT shell [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmetacharacters - insufficient for security[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mFilenameUtils.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: EXISTS but is NOT used in the vulnerable code [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath and doesn't cover all shell metacharacters[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **external2.ExternalParser**: Shows a BETTER approach using ProcessBuilder with [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mList<String>, but still relies on insufficient escaping[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Temporary File Creation**: Uses secure naming [0m[1;39m([0m[32m"apache-tika-"[0m[39m + random + [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msuffix[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but the USAGE of paths in commands is insecure[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **No Input Validation**: No validation occurs before paths are used in command [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstruction[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Critical Logic to Preserve[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **External Parser Functionality**: Must continue to support executing external [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcommands for parsing[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Token Replacement**: IN[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN and OUT[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN mechanism must [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwork[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Stream Handling**: Input/output stream processing logic must remain intact[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Backward Compatibility**: Existing configurations and command templates should[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontinue to work[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Parser Chain**: The delegation and parser selection mechanism must not be [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbroken[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Primary Fix: Secure Command Execution in ExternalParser[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/parser/external/ExternalParser.java` [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m280[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m318[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Approach**: Replace the vulnerable command construction and execution logic with [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma secure implementation that uses ProcessBuilder properly and validates file paths.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Steps**:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Remove String Splitting** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m290[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m291[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the dangerous `command[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.split[0m[1;39m([0m[32m" "[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` logic[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Treat the entire command array as-is, where each element is already a separate[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39margument[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This ensures proper command structure is maintained[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Implement Secure Token Replacement** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m296[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m306[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace the simple `[0m[1;35mString.replace[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with a secure substitution method[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Before substitution, validate that file paths contain only safe characters[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Use a whitelist approach: allow only alphanumeric, dash, underscore, period, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mforward slash, and backslash[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Reject paths containing shell metacharacters: `;`, `|`, `&`, `$`, `` ` ``, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;39m([0m[39m`, `[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `<`, `>`, `*`, `?`, `[0m[1;39m[[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`, `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`, `\n`, `\r`, etc.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If validation fails, throw a TikaException with a clear security error message[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Use ProcessBuilder Exclusively** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m308[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m318[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove `[0m[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls entirely [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m311[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m315[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Always use `ProcessBuilder` with the command array [0m[1;39m([0m[39mList or array form[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ProcessBuilder with array/list arguments does NOT invoke a shell by default[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Each array element becomes a separate argv[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m parameter, preventing command [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minjection[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd.length == [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         process = [0m[1;35mRuntime.getRuntime[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         process = [0m[1;35mRuntime.getRuntime[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - With:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ProcessBuilder processBuilder = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     process = [0m[1;35mprocessBuilder.start[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Add Path Validation Method**:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Create a new private method `[0m[1;35mvalidateFilePath[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString path[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` that:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Checks if path contains only whitelisted characters[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Verifies path is absolute [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot relative with `..`[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Ensures path length is reasonable [0m[1;39m([0m[39m< [0m[1;36m4096[0m[39m chars[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Throws TikaException if validation fails[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Call this method before using paths in token replacement[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Preserve Error Handling**:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keep the existing try-catch structure [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m316[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m318[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m320[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m360[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure exceptions from validation are properly propagated[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Maintain the existing stream processing logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m320[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m360[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Implementation Details[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**New Validation Method** [0m[1;39m([0m[39madd after line [0m[1;36m278[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m * Validates that a file path is safe to use in external command execution.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m * Prevents command injection by ensuring path contains only safe characters.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m * [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m * @param path the file path to validate[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m * @throws TikaException if the path contains unsafe characters[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate void [0m[1;35mvalidateFilePath[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString path[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws TikaException [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpath == null || [0m[1;35mpath.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"File path cannot be null or empty"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check for absolute path to prevent directory traversal[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    File file = new [0m[1;35mFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mfile.isAbsolute[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"File path must be absolute: "[0m[39m + path[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Whitelist of safe characters: alphanumeric, basic punctuation, path [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mseparators[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Explicitly exclude shell metacharacters[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    String unsafeChars = [0m[32m";|&$`[0m[32m([0m[32m)[0m[32m<>*?[0m[32m[[0m[32m][0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m'\"\n\r\t\\x00-\\x1F"[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar c : [0m[1;35mpath.toCharArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35munsafeChars.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || [0m[1;35mCharacter.isISOControl[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[32m"File path contains unsafe character: "[0m[39m + [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mInteger.toHexString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[32m" in path: "[0m[39m + path[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Additional safety: check path length[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpath.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;36m4096[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"File path exceeds maximum length"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modified [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Method** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m280[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m318[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate void [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaInputStream stream, XHTMLContentHandler xhtml, Metadata [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmetadata,[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   TemporaryResources tmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException, SAXException, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTikaException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    boolean inputToStdIn = true;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    boolean outputFromStdOut = true;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    boolean hasPatterns = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmetadataPatterns != null && [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m![0m[1;35mmetadataPatterns.isEmpty[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    File output = null;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Build our command - DO NOT split strings, use array as-is[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    String[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m cmd;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcommand.length == [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m REMOVED: cmd = command[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.split[0m[1;39m([0m[32m" "[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Security fix: treat as single command, don't split[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmd = new String[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m command[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmd = new String[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mcommand.length[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mSystem.arraycopy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcommand, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, cmd, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, command.length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Validate and replace tokens[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint i = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < cmd.length; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mIN[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            String inputPath = [0m[1;35mstream.getFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mvalidateFilePath[0m[1;39m([0m[39minputPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Security validation[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            cmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = cmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.replace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mIN[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN, inputPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            inputToStdIn = false;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mOUT[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            output = [0m[1;35mtmp.createTemporaryFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            String outputPath = [0m[1;35moutput.getPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mvalidateFilePath[0m[1;39m([0m[39moutputPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Security validation[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            outputFromStdOut = false;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            cmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = cmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.replace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mOUT[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN, outputPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Execute using ProcessBuilder [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmore secure than Runtime.exec[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Process process = null;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ProcessBuilder processBuilder = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        process = [0m[1;35mprocessBuilder.start[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"problem with process exec"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Failed to execute external command"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Rest of the method remains unchanged [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m320[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m360[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39minputToStdIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35msendInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mprocess, stream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mprocess.getOutputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.close[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m existing stream processing code [0m[33m...[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m finally [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mprocess.waitFor[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInterruptedException ignore[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!outputFromStdOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mFileInputStream fileInputStream = new [0m[1;35mFileInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39moutput[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mextractOutput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfileInputStream, xhtml[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Is the Optimal Solution[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Addresses Root Cause**: Directly fixes the unsafe path usage and command [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexecution[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Uses ProcessBuilder Correctly**: ProcessBuilder with array arguments doesn't [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoke shell, preventing metacharacter interpretation[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Validates Input**: The [0m[1;35mvalidateFilePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method prevents malicious paths from[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreaching command execution[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Maintains Functionality**: Preserves the token replacement mechanism and all [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting features[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Backward Compatible**: Existing command templates continue to work [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexcept [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthose relying on shell features like wildcards[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Defense in Depth**: Multiple layers of protection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvalidation + [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Clear Error Messages**: Security violations result in clear TikaException [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmessages[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. **No Breaking Changes**: Doesn't modify parser selection, delegation, or [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfiguration mechanisms[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m9[0m[39m. **Follows Java Best Practices**: ProcessBuilder is the recommended way to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexecute external processes securely[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Command Templates Using Shell Features**: [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Issue**: Templates relying on shell wildcards, pipes, or redirects will [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbreak[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: These were insecure by design; users should update templates [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto use direct commands[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Documentation**: Clearly document that shell features are not supported for [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msecurity reasons[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Single-String Commands**:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Issue**: Commands specified as single strings with spaces were previously [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msplit[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Update documentation to require proper array format for [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmulti-argument commands[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Migration**: Provide examples of converting [0m[32m"command arg1 arg2"[0m[39m to [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m[[0m[32m"command"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"arg1"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"arg2"[0m[1;39m][0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Performance**:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Issue**: Validation adds minimal overhead[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Validation is [0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m where n is path length, negligible compared[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto process execution[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Path Length Limits**:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Issue**: Some systems allow very long paths[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: [0m[1;36m4096[0m[39m character limit is reasonable for most use cases; can be [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmade configurable if needed[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Testing Recommendations[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Test with legitimate external parsers [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., tesseract, pdftotext[0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Test with paths containing spaces [0m[1;39m([0m[39mshould still work[0m[1;39m)[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Test with malicious paths containing shell metacharacters [0m[1;39m([0m[39mshould fail with [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTikaException[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Test data URI parsing with various content types[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Verify existing unit tests still pass[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Add security-specific test cases for command injection attempts[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Alternative Considered: Disabling External Parsers for Embedded Content[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn alternative would be to prevent ExternalParser from being invoked for embedded [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdocuments [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata URIs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. However, this would:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Break legitimate use cases where embedded documents need external parsers[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Be a workaround rather than a fix[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Still leave the vulnerability exploitable through other vectors[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe primary fix is superior because it makes ExternalParser secure for all use [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcases.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
