[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Use validated path[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        path = [0m[1;35mexiftoolPath.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSecurityException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Security manager denied access to path: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, path, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Error validating exiftool path: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, path, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    ExternalParser exifToolParser = [0m[1;35mgetExistingExifToolParser[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of method unchanged[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Defense-in-depth: Even system properties should be validated[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Prevents directory traversal, symlink attacks, and arbitrary executable execution[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Validates file existence and executability before use[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Ensures the executable is actually exiftool [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot arbitrary binary[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Part [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Fix [0m[1;35mresetExifTool[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Metadata Cleanup[0m                                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Part [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m: Defense-in-Depth - ExternalParser Hardening[0m                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `[0m[1;35mExternalParser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m280[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m319[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Issue [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m**: Space-splitting vulnerability at line [0m[1;36m291[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Current Code**:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcommand.length == [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    cmd = command[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.split[0m[1;39m([0m[32m" "[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fixed Code**:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcommand.length == [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Security: Do not split commands to prevent argument injection[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    cmd = new String[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m command[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Issue [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m**: Path validation before token replacement[0m                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint i = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < [0m[1;35mpath.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCharacter.isISOControl[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Reject shell metacharacters[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[32m";|&$`[0m[32m([0m[32m)[0m[32m<>*?[0m[32m[[0m[32m][0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m\'\""[0m[1;35m.indexOf[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[32m"File path contains unsafe character '"[0m[39m + c + [0m[32m"' at position "[0m[39m + [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mi[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Length check[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpath.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;36m4096[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"File path exceeds maximum length"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mApply validation in token replacement [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m296[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint i = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < cmd.length; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mIN[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        String inputPath = [0m[1;35mstream.getFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mvalidateFilePath[0m[1;39m([0m[39minputPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Add validation[0m                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mOUT[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        output = [0m[1;35mtmp.createTemporaryFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = cmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;35m.replace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mOUT[0m[1;33mPUT[0m[39m_FILE_TOKEN, outputPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        outputFromStdOut = false;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Issue [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m**: Use ProcessBuilder instead of [0m[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace execution code [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m308[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m318[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Execute using ProcessBuilder [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmore secure than Runtime.exec[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcess process = null;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtry [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    ProcessBuilder processBuilder = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    process = [0m[1;35mprocessBuilder.start[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Failed to start external process"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Failed to start external process"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ProcessBuilder is more secure and doesn't invoke shell[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throwing TikaException ensures failures are properly handled[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Validates file paths to prevent injection through path manipulation[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Security Boundary Enforcement[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Trusted Configuration Sources [0m[1;39m([0m[39mALLOWED[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- System properties: `[0m[1;35mSystem.getProperty[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"tika.exiftool.path"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Configuration files: XML resources in classpath[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Environment variables: `[0m[1;35mSystem.getenv[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"TIKA_EXIFTOOL_PATH"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Untrusted Sources [0m[1;39m([0m[39mBLOCKED[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Document metadata: `[0m[1;35mmetadata.get[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"html_meta:exiftool_path"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- User input from parsed content[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any data derived from document being parsed[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Preservation of Existing Functionality[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### What is Preserved:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Data URI scheme parsing continues to work[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Embedded JPEG extraction from HTML still functions[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. ExifTool can still be configured via system property[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Existing tests using proper configuration remain valid[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. All other HTML parsing features unaffected[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### What Changes:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Documents can no longer specify exiftool path [0m[1;39m([0m[39msecurity improvement[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Warning logs appear when documents attempt exiftool_path configuration[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Administrators must use `-Dtika.exiftool.path` system property if needed[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Invalid exiftool paths now properly rejected with logging[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Impact:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Breaking Change**: Any code relying on document-provided exiftool_path will [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstop working[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: This is intentional - it was a security vulnerability[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Documentation**: Clear migration guide for using system property[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Performance**: Additional validation adds minor overhead[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Validation only occurs during configuration, not per-document[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Impact**: Negligible - path validation is fast[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Compatibility**: Older documents with exiftool_path metadata will see warnings[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Warning only - parsing continues normally[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Benefit**: Helps identify potentially malicious documents[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Testing Considerations:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Verify compilation succeeds[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Ensure no syntax errors or duplicate declarations[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Test that html_met[0m[1;92ma:e[0m[39mxiftool_path is ignored[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Verify system property configuration still works[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Confirm validation rejects invalid paths[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check that existing HTML parsing tests pass[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Verify embedded image extraction works[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis fix strategy addresses both the compilation error and the security [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvulnerability through:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Correct Import Structure**: Adding necessary imports without syntax errors[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Security Boundary**: Blocking document metadata from controlling external [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcommands[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Trusted Configuration**: Using only system properties for exiftool path[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Defense-in-Depth**: Multiple validation layers in both HtmlHandler and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExternalParser[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Safe Execution**: Removing space-splitting and using ProcessBuilder[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Proper Cleanup**: Fixing metadata key in resetExifTool[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe approach prioritizes security while maintaining legitimate functionality and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprovides clear migration path for users.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
